import React from 'react'
import {  Route, Switch } from 'react-router-dom'

import { TeacherPage, StudentPage, TopPage } from '../pages'

import './App.css'

const App = (
  <Switch>
    <Route exact path="/" component={TopPage}/>
    <Route exact path="/live/:uuid/teacher" component={TeacherPage}/>
    <Route exact path="/live/:uuid/student" component={StudentPage}/>
  </Switch>
)

export default App
